@startuml

title Flow #1: Single DID for Agent. Step #1: Identity provisioning.

autonumber

TensorFlowAgent -> InterlinkedProtocolAgent : Request Identity
InterlinkedProtocolAgent -> InterlinkedProtocolAgent : Generate Mnemonic
InterlinkedProtocolAgent -> InterlinkedProtocolAgent : Generate HD mode
InterlinkedProtocolAgent -> InterlinkedProtocolAgent : Derive wallet using Mnemonic and index=0
InterlinkedProtocolAgent -> TensorFlowAgent : Response with Mnemonic, wallet keypair and index
TensorFlowAgent -> TensorFlowAgent : Store Mnemonic, wallet keypair and index securely

@enduml